    "content": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body class=\"tei-surface3\" id=\"srcD_surface_a18r\"><div class=\"content \"><pb-facs-link emit=\"transcription\" facs=\"https://ores.klassik-stiftung.de/digilib/Scaler/IIIF/gsa!Arbeitskopie!71!75094!75094_35\" style=\"float: right; margin-top: -2em;\">a18r</pb-facs-link><div id=\"srcD_surface_a18r\" class=\"transkriptionField\" style=\"\"><div id=\"srcD_zone_a18r_div2_d2e45\" style=\"padding-top:10em;padding-bottom:0em;\" class=\"singleBlock textBlock \" debug-msg=\"test\" data-debug=\"1\"><div id=\"srcD_zone_a18r_fw_d2e26\" class=\"fw-top-left\" style=\"\"></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a18r_fw_d2e29\" class=\"fw-top-right\" style=\"\"></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a18r_lb1\" class=\"note-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb1\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"top:4.375em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb1\" duration=\"5000\">1</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft hand N_black1 markLine\" style=\"margin-left:27em;\"><pb-highlight key=\"#mark1_a17r#mark1_a18r\" highlight-self=\"highlight-self\" duration=\"5000\">#</pb-highlight> auf <span class=\"tei-ref5\">Seite 13</span> einzuschieben!\n               \n                  </span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb2\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb2\" duration=\"5000\">2</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">aber <span id=\"PD43107N2l9l21l5l8l5\" class=\"hatching\">es ist</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l21l5l8l5\"><span class=\"transcription\">es ist</span></pb-popover> besser<span class=\"insertionMark right beforePunctuation insertion-above \" style=\"top:0em;height:1.3125em;\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:-1em;\"> ist es</span></span>, daß es uns eine in solchen Dingen nicht zu unterschätzende Autorität ausdrücklich bezeugt, <span class=\"latin\">Thomas von Aquino</span>, \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb3\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb3\" duration=\"5000\">3</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">der große Lehrer und Heilige. „<span class=\"latin\">Beati in regno coelesti</span>, sagt er sanft wie ein Lamm, <span class=\"latin\">videbunt poenas damnatorum, </span><span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\"><span class=\"latin\">ut</span></span> \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb4\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb4\" duration=\"5000\">4</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"latin\"><span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">beatitudo</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">illis</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">magis</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">complaceat</span></span>.“ Oder will man es in einer stärkeren Tonart hören, etwa aus dem Munde eines \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb5\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb5\" duration=\"5000\">5</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">triumphirenden Kirchenvaters, der seinen Christen die grausamen Wollüste der öffentlichen Schauspiele widerrieth – warum \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb6\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb6\" duration=\"5000\">6</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">doch? „Der Glaube bietet uns ja viel mehr, <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-above \" style=\"top:0em;height:1.3125em;\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:-6.2em;\">– sagt er <span class=\"latin\">de spectac. c. 29 ss.</span> –</span></span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">viel Stärkeres</span>; Dank der Erlösung stehen uns ja ganz andre Freu-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb7\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb7\" duration=\"5000\">7</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">den zu Gebote; an Stelle der Athleten haben wir unsre Märtyrer; wollen wir Blut, nun, so haben wir das \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb8\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb8\" duration=\"5000\">8</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">Blut Christi… Aber was erwartet uns erst am Tage seiner Wiederkunft, seines Triumphes!“ – und nun fährt er \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb9\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb9\" duration=\"5000\">9</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">fort, der entzückte Visionär –&nbsp;<span class=\"latin\">at enim supersunt alia spectacula, ille ultimus et perpetuus judicii dies, ille nati</span><span class=\"latin\">-</span>\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb10\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb10\" duration=\"5000\">10</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"latin\">onibus insperatus, ille derisus, cum tanta saeculi vetustas et tot ejus nativitates uno igne haurientur. Quae tunc \n                  </span></span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb11\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb11\" duration=\"5000\">11</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"latin\">spectaculi latitudo! <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Quid</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">admirer</span>! <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Quid</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">rideam</span>! <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Ubi</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">gaudeam</span>! <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Ubi</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">exultem</span>, spectans tot et tantos reges, qui \n                  </span></span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb12\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb12\" duration=\"5000\">12</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"latin\">in coelum recepti nuntiabantur, cum ipso Jove et ipsis suis testibus in imis tenebris congemescentes! Item prae-\n                  </span></span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb13\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb13\" duration=\"5000\">13</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"latin\">sides</span> (die Provincialstatthalter) persecutores dominici nominis saevioribus quam ipsi flammis saevierunt insultantibus \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb14\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb14\" duration=\"5000\">14</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"latin\">contra Christianos liquescentes! Quos praeterea sapientes illos philosophos coram discipulis suis una conflagrantibus \n                  </span></span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb15\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb15\" duration=\"5000\">15</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"latin\">erubescentes, quibus nihil ad deum pertinere suadebant, quibus animas aut nullas aut non in pristina corpora reditu-\n                  </span></span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb16\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb16\" duration=\"5000\">16</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"latin\">ras affirmabant! Etiam poetas non ad Rhadamanti nec ad Minois, sed ad inopinati Christi tribunal palpitantes!</span> \n                  \n                     </span></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a18r_lb17\" class=\"note-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a18r_lb17\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"bottom:-0.1em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a18r_lb17\" duration=\"5000\">17</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft hand N_black1 \" style=\"margin-left:44.9625em;\"><span class=\"latin\">v.s.</span></span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a18r_fw_d2e37\" class=\"fw-bottom-left\" style=\"\"></div></div></div></div></body></html>",
